@startuml ProjectStates
title Lifecycle of a Project (IR-Board)

state Active

State Finished: Completed

State Deactivated: Cancelled/postponed

State Removed: Hidden from sight, archived


' Transiciones
[*] -down-> Active: Project creation

Active -right-> Finished
Finished -left-> Active

Active --> Deactivated
Deactivated --> Active

Deactivated --> Removed
Removed --> Deactivated

Removed --> [*]: Purged from archive

@enduml